  PREFERRED_DIAG_LIBRARY DLAF
  PRINT_LEVEL low
  PROJECT H2O-6
  &TIMINGS
    THRESHOLD 0.0
  &END TIMINGS
&END GLOBAL

&FORCE_EVAL
